{"tid":1645792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"庫克：遭下架港警位置應用程式涉違反法律","createTime":"2019-10-11T04:23:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T04:30:15.000Z","uid":252013,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"79cc56f65425b30c1866a69209eb18e8e7aa0547","tid":1645792,"uid":252013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T04:23:23.000Z","msg":"Tim Cook....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蘋果公司行政總裁庫克向員工發內部信件，為早前公司下架實時顯示香港警方位置應用程式的決定護航。<br />\n庫克指，公司近日收到由警方及香港用戶提供的可靠資訊，認為應用程式將會用作惡意針對個別警察，或於未有警員出現的地方侵害個別人士及財產，違反本地法律，在諮詢過政府部門後決定將相關程式下架。<br />\n庫克形容有關決定並不容易，但相信決定最能保障客戶，公司會繼續調查事件。<br />\n...<a href=\"https://headline.appt.cf/share.php?a=headlinewwd&amp;id=105935\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fheadline.appt.cf%2Fshare.php%3Fa%3Dheadlinewwd%26id%3D105935&d=tgdX0zC4r3YoKKw%2Bq%2FbDqb9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=281252c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://headline.appt.cf/share.php?a=headlinewwd&amp;id=105935</a>"},{"pid":"ee74beaac92644ba538aad8042a36a9079172852","tid":1645792,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T04:24:51.000Z","msg":"連登仔 你唔係仲用apple下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a15061a162033dce328e2f01a3784c62fdd039f","tid":1645792,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee74beaac92644ba538aad8042a36a9079172852","tid":1645792,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T04:24:51.000Z","msg":"連登仔 你唔係仲用apple下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T04:25:32.000Z","msg":"iPhone安全 popo 破解唔到"},{"pid":"5506437b781626b963d0c72bba889cf155cf7bdc","tid":1645792,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T04:30:15.000Z","msg":"快啲follow<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/RebelPepperWang\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRebelPepperWang&d=tgdX0zC4r3YoKKw%2Bq%2FbDqb9ZTfDhdy